data.name: metroLabel1.Text
data.value: Welcome to nosue! nosue!lazer is another nosue! project that supports osu!lazer. We supports following clients: osu!, osu!lazer, osu!droid, opsu! In order to play nosue!, You need to switch your osu! server first. It can be done by changing your DNS server or add entries to hosts manually, but it might silly. Just turn on nosue!lazer and HTTPS, and You're done! If you want to back to osu! official server, Just turn off nosue!lazer! You do not need to turn off HTTPS. Thanks for play nosue!
